---
title: Carb Smart Beyond Meat® and Sweet Potato Salad with Creamy Herbed Sun-Dried Tomato Dressing
description: A generous drizzle of creamy and herby sun-dried tomato dressing is the star of this dish. Smoky Beyond Meat® is cooked and tossed with roasted sweet potatoes, tangy marinated radishes and a salad topper, making a meal that only skimps on carbs, not flavour.

